@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bring Costco to Stillwater, OK</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #c8102e;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 50px;
            gap: 40px;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .section:nth-child(even) {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .text h2 {
            color: #c8102e;
        }

        .image {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .section {
                flex-direction: column !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Why Costco Should Come to Stillwater, Oklahoma</h1>
</header>

<!-- Section 1 -->
<div class="section">
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607082349566-187342175e2f" alt="Open land">
    </div>
    <div class="text">
        <h2>Plenty of Space for Development!</h2>
        <p>
            Stillwater, Oklahoma offers a significant amount of open land that is ideal for large-scale retail development.
            Costco warehouses require substantial space for both the building and parking, and Stillwater has multiple
            areas that could easily accommodate this need. With ongoing growth and expansion, the city is well-positioned
            to support a major retailer like Costco without the limitations seen in more densely populated areas.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Section 2 -->
<div class="section">
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586201375761-83865001e31c" alt="Shopping cart">
    </div>
    <div class="text">
        <h2>No Large Bulk Competition</h2>
        <p>
            One of the biggest advantages of bringing Costco to Stillwater is the lack of direct competition in the bulk
            retail space. While there are grocery stores and smaller retailers, there is no major warehouse club like Costco
            or Sam’s Club currently serving the area. This gives Costco a unique opportunity to dominate the market and
            establish a strong customer base with minimal resistance.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Section 3 -->
<div class="section">
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556740738-b6a63e27c4df" alt="Money and shopping">
    </div>
    <div class="text">
        <h2>Strong Regional Spending Power</h2>
        <p>
            Stillwater is not just supported by its local population—it also benefits from its proximity to larger cities
            like Tulsa, Dallas, and Oklahoma City. Visitors, students, and traveling professionals bring additional income
            into the area, creating strong purchasing power. This consistent flow of money makes Stillwater an attractive
            location for a high-volume retailer like Costco, ensuring steady demand and long-term success.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>Bring Costco to Stillwater — It's Time!</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
